

Here are the Steps

go to the Git Settings

from the left explore  : select GIT (just above the
Credential)

click upon "Edit Systemwide gitconfig" button

this will open 2 notepad automatically

one is gitconfig text file (Administrator)

another one is config text file (Administrator)

do the following in config text file// paste
        sslVerify = false just below
the sslCAInfo line.

[http] 

        sslCAInfo =
D:/Git/mingw64/ssl/certs/ca-bundle.crt 

        sslVerify = false

 

